<br>
In guild groups, though, in general, parchments are randomed between the casters that need spells of that parchment's level, melee items are nbg to the melee in the group, then randomed for at the end (if not no drop) by those wanting to use for twinkage or to sell.<br>
<br>
It's not hard.<br>
